{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.1,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "output_format": "pcm_44100",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Last Friday, the Dynamous community ran a ninety-minute interactive workshop with Cole Medin on something most AI coding content gets wrong.",
      "checksum": "sha256:840275c5584dacc8ba1c196dbe562e60ed1c51d6771c74d0158e2b010c13030e",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 7.662585034013605,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "The codebase. Ninety-seven Dynamous members in the room.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ab03651eaef2968e52082aa6b70ff6e33aa7afd040955879ca2368699b16f041",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 21
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Six strategies. This video is the quick summary.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5ebeeeb3cede5e5b861e018d3e446e14be6d85dd191a1be57840ac4f515809b1",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 29
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Here's the problem. Vibe coding doesn't scale.",
      "checksum": "sha256:19925efd14b6d5ce79c2eb3ff9d2e3b136c6d2f55e76a5e5c45907b9b4808b2c",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 37
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Every team starts simple. A clean greenfield.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2fc8721fa1c09678e2d2faf85e1ad0c743fefde4884153db52533e12c4ffbb2a",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 44
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "One Claude Code session. Smooth shipping.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a46606b7d43db8c50f32d7eab028b744679a81e72b4c03618c6b120102ff6295",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 51
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "But it always ends in two-thousand-line god components.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b4b89703e193b5f9995929acc2532cbc91ca074705c16799a20f29121a92ec8e",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 57
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Agents hallucinating patterns you never showed them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ec53f33b7f3c6ce99633baa1d23bf9d7e34a8cb956dca300887f42fe14b135ac",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 65
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Context bloat killing every session. And one specific failure mode is killing people.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5738b8e8f3539d6dbcd5d21fa4ce1a0249d4720260bc09e3ec72b51bc2caea72",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 72
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "A bad prime command. Some teams run a prime, and it pulls in tens of thousands of tokens before they've written a single line of code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:df200ea71863f69e0f5803a726f24a5ed4e5237b7a2977fb185659a704c85795",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 7.430385487528345,
      "word_count": 26,
      "words_offset": 85
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "The agent's context is its most precious resource.",
      "checksum": "sha256:73c43da3992da0f447e678e8505fe61aee271e25ee698b520b7f1e8d8fdf6b52",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 111
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Pre-bloat it, and reasoning quality collapses.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fbe82f0ee9acb6bcd8bce0e8139ec5b0462ef414364b436a9a2a3cbec22f2b95",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 119
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "You're already losing. Here's the pivot.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1c976f608a21e2d950cc3adab8c7551e98d318af6021e0bbfc04de1770f08997",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 125
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "File size isn't the right metric. A two-thousand-line file with three imports is fine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:20266656ba2fc4ee81ee69ac59977a56934598a625c70cdff977c0b317de173f",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 5.61922902494331,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 131
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "A five-hundred-line file imported by twenty others is a fire.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4d4e97ba315a1fbb2befd2ac1c17a7983d7a6fb6978a435037e205adfe6aeafb",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 145
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Coupling, not lines. Six strategies. Each one stands alone.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a255b6ebd89ff34cdb9cc721c6a83ef39e1b782b505c3a3f885d53cb1e567af5",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 155
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Combined, they turn any messy codebase into something an agent can actually navigate.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cfcc3e399551579942738fd127f17fe9daceaa818f1b003558e47095a22b6777",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 164
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "One \u2014 vertical slice architecture. Organize by feature, not by layer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8f148fadab5927b91fc237b138d3ec0b35e37460d87a0e95afa13bec0ac84a09",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 177
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Two \u2014 brownfield day one. Use parallel sub-agents to derive the AI layer the first time.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8536544cdec07fcb7be0b4f5b61c9a3d2923d92987a654319439d3c94ec453db",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 5.758548752834467,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 188
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Three \u2014 context management. Three tiers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:44823c227d1534aec23c4cf97741b03cc2a2fc3ac69a38f494e48eb68bca2624",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 204
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Four \u2014 focused priming. One prime command per slice.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7d709184782e11f42d04f2974213c3d765a60021376dd598912c926a18374fcf",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 210
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Five \u2014 parallel worktrees. Multiple agents, isolated copies, zero collisions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c5e8ec187204b082517bf0348294512b25ad4cb287a61974d2759d37c979a08d",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 5.015510204081632,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 219
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Six \u2014 coupling over line count. Strategy one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d15de497866f2f7f41aeb9c61b5cd34160745dcf98a8560c59196ebad1d8f2fe",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 229
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Vertical slice architecture. Most codebases are organized by layer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:12c4f25a7dce26aaf6a87c306c05be9e6949d8baeaa73b0f55821ccf6b82135c",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 237
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Controllers in one folder. Services in another.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fcbb59f4c063b3a37b772c8e0e45461d46b553fbe92ec6508f5e013d22657e9f",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 246
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "Repositories in a third. Tests way over there.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e0f74ef92644e67d9f22d28150a5d1cff9ca2d35285d8ff453df7f75c6f1921f",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 253
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "That's fine for humans who already have the system in their head.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a8b3f9037bc35213b3df0c6c42ef5a2b299fdc7d3b496fbf7d5337f4185e3012",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 261
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "It's terrible for a coding agent. To touch one feature, the agent chases that feature across four folders, burning tokens at every hop.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c89701c5529d2fc9f0058d90e20c2b0427849211b8383b109ca8d355ef804361",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 8.034104308390022,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 273
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Vertical slice flips it. One folder per feature, owning everything that feature needs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:273d17f3285112c59063d2f8300bd1519abc0bc1d251b425917c69ecec43eb6d",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 296
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Models. Schemas. Routes. Service. Errors.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a8df151653acb1a8f2709f98c203f01454918db2dc38a027bbfda7528497a20c",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 309
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Tests. All in one place. The agent loads the slice, has the full feature in context, ships.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b81e5b300332ccfdd26b03634cee3289dc5394051947d3c779df8b8d97541369",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 6.2693877551020405,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 314
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "And here's the part most senior engineers get wrong.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8c81707fe6f4b3e6f52facacc109439c9690ddbbfd191e85441d4a593a18b988",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 331
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "You don't refactor everything. Start with the next new feature.",
      "checksum": "sha256:89212e38d304dd6b18e3c21c103f02bfdd76c5d0d28c165f91e8b9cb0de101c6",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 340
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "Build it in the vertical slice shape. Let the brownfield decay around it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f08c68b843bb04e61d6a3d6f08873a5bd32046240f8507809e2138532822d195",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 350
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "Six months later, every new feature ships vertical slice, and you've quietly migrated.\n\nStrategy two.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c53a45d1d30b2a8b5b4a4143fa10e40f290e2025458c1c09c9a6ecc72e81ba3b",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 7.987664399092971,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 363
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "Most engineers conflate two different scenarios into one word \u2014 brownfield.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b3065b88b66160ef14e468e14ae26f2fe52e7f6960474555eaedd77b9e66cd6f",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 378
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "Type A \u2014 there's no AI layer yet. The agent walks in blind.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ebd42f62c93e76b0d628760519f52c14e4b7e12351d541a7df5734226183f4ca",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 389
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "You do this once, ever, per codebase. Spin up parallel explorer sub-agents.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bd859d9ae2d8f24d4cea9f3072ff370a0af54b3eb5e95fb96397a9a39931fb28",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 5.015510204081632,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 402
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Five for small. Eight or ten for a sprawling monorepo.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1d0a3c12660105af7aac6cc963d996c378623913c7aee21196072f968518e94c",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 414
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "Each one investigates one slice. They converge into a single codebase-analysis markdown.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9160ace6e66e0aa69b26f44748d6735df6a319f8c5a0795f91c6987555467f06",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 5.572789115646258,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 424
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "Then a second round of builder sub-agents derive your global rules plus a customized command suite.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1b5af7c2ab202624de4c4e804b3833100913fd80936d938612cf6a7fd5d1ebf9",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 436
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "Ten minutes. Done forever. Type B \u2014 the AI layer exists.",
      "checksum": "sha256:02f70a825206bff3b1f95f27be02bf52850259bdba8550f1198ae3218d75aad0",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 452
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "New epic incoming. This is where you live ninety-five percent of the time.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f0f4a2eb747380e16a12e81948eed340b11713b08452fb83cb8e89e09f9ee1da",
      "wav": "chunk-42.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 463
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "text": "Every sprint reads the layer. Edits where reality has drifted. Ships.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cde8adc7e43f4e0f66fff54219dccf5f0ccbb9b5fd5d8d664e5718108a1b751f",
      "wav": "chunk-43.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 476
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "text": "Loops back. And a question came up in the chat.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6f89902721e914d64392f9944d89ef2f3558600453b5c6f7782bf08ba064d48f",
      "wav": "chunk-44.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 487
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "text": "How do you know if the AI layer is trustworthy?",
      "checksum": "sha256:3a461b9fc22716f47ade6776cdb7473d96d21cbb7c9e359757a1e0d2a5db6101",
      "wav": "chunk-45.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 497
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "text": "Run the fill-gaps audit. Same parallel sub-agents pattern.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5b0165ef06d42a48cbdca677a96787b12d32463483035ffec1c8cc9da4833380",
      "wav": "chunk-46.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 507
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "text": "Different goal. The agent compares what the layer claims against the actual code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2c82e2a180005b197159ac2b2fc959cd84e660a4f704d49d5da76973054694cb",
      "wav": "chunk-47.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 515
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "text": "Surfaces drift. Closes gaps. Strategy three.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c3530000e7bd31fcc0d3871ad4e3fbf6ce613139347b7906ebf9134b0da75d1a",
      "wav": "chunk-48.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 528
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "text": "Context management. Every codebase has three structurally different kinds of context.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b4843e005b0d9e04ac7e89930ba08d1474c3c255414d172e31e891b3fbabedf5",
      "wav": "chunk-49.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 534
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "text": "Global. On-demand. And Layer Two. Global is auto-loaded every session.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d54b82fc77136b74c41f9d6767248e7e8a79750ec02be9233a39727636049d22",
      "wav": "chunk-50.wav",
      "duration": 5.201269841269841,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 545
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "text": "Tech stack. Code style. Must-know conventions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d61db5a1fd5c779928fb6305e8dcbb39379a03e5ad9190a1be5a96e33f73489a",
      "wav": "chunk-51.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 555
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "text": "Keep this under three hundred lines. On-demand is loaded only when relevant.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c05e5b1e65d0d823eab42d0dc6069a44a17e5945e663ed24691dd2a7a2157ca0",
      "wav": "chunk-52.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 561
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "text": "Pattern guides. Per-feature READMEs. Layer Two is the plan for this specific ticket.",
      "checksum": "sha256:55a05be71517310c6b2476e209f20c91aaf388ceab9f677720fb3303c61edae9",
      "wav": "chunk-53.wav",
      "duration": 5.804988662131519,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 573
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "text": "Loaded once. Discarded after. If you put everything in global, you pay a token tax every session for context that's irrelevant ninety percent of the time.",
      "checksum": "sha256:85bdfe2a23a51be7acbaad5dcc25909d13d9c402346b12e6ec98a64e2bc8a0bc",
      "wav": "chunk-54.wav",
      "duration": 10.263219954648527,
      "word_count": 26,
      "words_offset": 586
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "text": "And another chat question \u2014 markdown or HTML?",
      "checksum": "sha256:5de4ce0983d2ee1777da0bc3a0f83e17bba26e16113fe70279a2281d0e90a457",
      "wav": "chunk-55.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 612
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "text": "Markdown wins. HTML burns tokens for layout you don't need.\n\nStrategy four.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ee2912df4e929eb0885def9e5e3fa12e69ec940f6d739d66a4f8ffc3d4f39877",
      "wav": "chunk-56.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 620
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "text": "Focused priming. A vanilla prime command tries to read the whole project.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7800111f18f55697ca87a4c13c13cdeaafb692e4b3fe93f0fc8d0ea67395fabd",
      "wav": "chunk-57.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 632
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "text": "On a small codebase, manageable. On a five-hundred-thousand-line monorepo, you blow the context budget before the task starts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5aa77ca9c24982ad536bc1f0c7083e455ca3715d34acbc0a79a0b682dff604d1",
      "wav": "chunk-58.wav",
      "duration": 7.987664399092971,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 644
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "text": "The fix is a family of prime commands. Each loads one slice.",
      "checksum": "sha256:16b4c898ac9a77bc1c98c3399dd4075d840bfffad51422200ed9b2d85abdbc10",
      "wav": "chunk-59.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 662
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "text": "Prime-server loads the backend. Prime-client loads the frontend.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5a3048589c4bd5bc3e292b5963578065edd39a4d274ba002d0353562ab5cfeea",
      "wav": "chunk-60.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 674
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "text": "Prime-components for shared UI. Prime-endpoint for adding a new A P I route end-to-end.",
      "checksum": "sha256:93d703fbf4141dff1bec0522c966e7ef092c7b1bfe6a56a44aa3d2021a3c646e",
      "wav": "chunk-61.wav",
      "duration": 5.340589569160998,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 682
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "text": "Each command loads five to ten files. The agent comes online with the right context for one type of task.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1a2f28d4d8d171d794e22792a914fa7055d78acab24e43546cd8d5d2c62a79a4",
      "wav": "chunk-62.wav",
      "duration": 5.851428571428571,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 696
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "text": "And who writes these prime commands? You let the brownfield-day-one skill generate them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4804c73808cacb645234aeea83d7dbc1426ef649c97540a51578b589ef0872c5",
      "wav": "chunk-63.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 716
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "text": "From your codebase. Customized. Day one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:41a0ac4aa77bf82de8e6564db338d34f947038bfa0f92902c83f21dc20f8e85c",
      "wav": "chunk-64.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 729
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "text": "And the workflow inside every ticket is the same three-move loop.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9d68fd9f71db732756c4f5dc9511e4fac58c9988985ced3e2e7ec154dd4f560c",
      "wav": "chunk-65.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 735
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "text": "You plan. Vertical-slice the work. Write the spec in its own session.",
      "checksum": "sha256:53a00d1b63d04724df550b75fa6c00c484b2a6cd7e0c008050e611b450e1ad0a",
      "wav": "chunk-66.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 746
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "text": "Sub-agents scout. Then Claude implements.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d4ba3fab51fd0b90a331046e6a034ae411d97f4103c14e16f88bcf1517d2c611",
      "wav": "chunk-67.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 758
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "text": "Fresh session. Only the plan loaded. Then you validate.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cc71214b925c9b7222229ff56ce571ec2a199ebf2e4131e07a79cb864429bc70",
      "wav": "chunk-68.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 763
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "text": "Lint. Type-check. Unit. End-to-end. Manual review.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6e004760adae202b2cfa1636574e8d40eeb7b056ad219d3d5298a91bfbbd7b1a",
      "wav": "chunk-69.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 772
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "text": "Five steps. Not eight. Not twelve. Five is the ceiling.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1c42a6692b192bf2b515b6c0581948b7ed90050cfbd84745ecf8468c86f7c604",
      "wav": "chunk-70.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 778
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "text": "Anything past that is over-engineering. Strategy five.",
      "checksum": "sha256:af6ee34bdf450b3ad604c92d829457016e68bf28117d01413139da6bb68fd9ad",
      "wav": "chunk-71.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 788
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "text": "Parallel worktrees. Same wallet, faster delivery.",
      "checksum": "sha256:425736d5a2a6539ac56235f08c14fc90d308c49042a5faf39a244d6e96e6cd2d",
      "wav": "chunk-72.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 795
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "text": "Git worktrees give you N working directories from the same repo.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a617a698550f0b16ff0f2921aea2f800f865b4489955a74c628e967630753002",
      "wav": "chunk-73.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 801
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "text": "Each on its own branch. Each isolated. Combine with multiple Claude Code sessions, and you have N parallel agentic streams.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c712aeb12b6c75571dd17e99a773622348e827ffa86fdab70f74f978db7887d9",
      "wav": "chunk-74.wav",
      "duration": 7.801904761904762,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 812
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "text": "Two terminals. Two tickets. Two pull requests.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a21f37126e84db03bfaa20c28b74e1e50bd3345f37996866e07785de17b6994e",
      "wav": "chunk-75.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 832
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "text": "No cross-talk. People assume parallel sessions equal N times the cost.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b1d707b2cec70c985c70c9c650f1a2c6b1031a5fc9f6462580fb6996610d17b9",
      "wav": "chunk-76.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 839
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "text": "Not really. The total work is the same total tokens.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cdf9390a3539b9c24e593cd8b4bc53a5c6b7f5dd1ab622049f0c328c8e4b66ff",
      "wav": "chunk-77.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 850
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "text": "You're compressing wallclock by running concurrently.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cd9dd6cb784f4d58b2024d0062a334fee158569f6b4e86439a79f4339ddb5e12",
      "wav": "chunk-78.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 860
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "text": "The constraint isn't your spend. It's how fast you can review and merge.",
      "checksum": "sha256:830eb72eb7a4a0cd92bfcdd6e7a3f5960edb1dde139ce28fc87f59921b3b4c03",
      "wav": "chunk-79.wav",
      "duration": 3.900952380952381,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 866
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "text": "Most teams find their bottleneck is the human reviewer, not the agent.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8e6ef8971f08d964c2f5d66b57771c56c7e3de869449367fde952b0de80e9ecc",
      "wav": "chunk-80.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 879
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "text": "Strategy six. Component sizing by coupling, not by line count.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5f9044270480d9bd482a0e59c1d4f38cded9d4323a1200e673f696b6d44260e9",
      "wav": "chunk-81.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 891
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "text": "The god-component anti-pattern is what kills your AI workflow.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b7c66135e1f1fdfc85ee1c775d3bf9c4076e43ead10d4c328fce94e58da3b773",
      "wav": "chunk-82.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 901
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "text": "Three questions. One. Can you work on this file in isolation?",
      "checksum": "sha256:55c650daecd2b34e9ff9895467d6ad24623f1765e53cf45a28a06422dfff7f88",
      "wav": "chunk-83.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 910
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "text": "Or do you always need to also load three other files to make sense of it?",
      "checksum": "sha256:28834e835572826986e55c50b897ff50fa344195e978eb8eab9c58a489941c7b",
      "wav": "chunk-84.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 921
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "text": "Two. Does the agent have clear boundaries?",
      "checksum": "sha256:47c0cc4dce820f52937e29caaf194b89c95b8179167725c258c37a3e2277164d",
      "wav": "chunk-85.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 937
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "text": "Or does every change ripple outside the file?",
      "checksum": "sha256:95c573bab270df7ac8efe7d582badb9b4eb67b8d7bdd2425e3457e2309d93f69",
      "wav": "chunk-86.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 944
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "text": "Three. Is the public A P I obvious? If any answer is no, the component is too coupled. Regardless of how many lines.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8ea958c713d8a5f2a9be84a5ba6bd2e1fdd2debeadabc91456097da68f175a6a",
      "wav": "chunk-87.wav",
      "duration": 7.801904761904762,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 952
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "text": "And finding unused code? AST-grep. It walks the codebase as an abstract syntax tree.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d0600e1db56e2c0eddecc7e0356bb7e40d01d5a58dd789cb29459eb5c1407f8b",
      "wav": "chunk-88.wav",
      "duration": 5.6656689342403626,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 975
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "text": "Anything with no inbound references is dead.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8b676889a6cde7b2918cf8aedaf230486ecdc80d01ce68658be77671f4600742",
      "wav": "chunk-89.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 989
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "text": "Pair it with your validate step. And here's the principle that landed hardest.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e1fb08c3be34a3b34e410f579bd75641f3b46aa0e7b64da233795a0fc8e6ab7c",
      "wav": "chunk-90.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 996
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "text": "Anthropic's own guidance on Claude Code in large codebases points to the same pattern.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f5fe0ac4c4e70223b2a06029504620ef51c0d8d87bf86770dc6188b51010b6d5",
      "wav": "chunk-91.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 1009
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "text": "Split exploration from editing. Your primary session edits files.",
      "checksum": "sha256:96fcb77624997deb85434c476ceeaab2d247036c0724c6c72993bdc36502419f",
      "wav": "chunk-92.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 1023
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "text": "Sub-agents take the context hit. The most precious resource when you're working with a coding agent isn't your wallet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e9cdaf8e0384ff51c7def9aad236f4924a790b91550ace9fe01524d54f6121fc",
      "wav": "chunk-93.wav",
      "duration": 7.291065759637188,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 1032
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "text": "It's the context. Protect it like a finite tank.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d88f2e564e601b02d5647478461a3436b64c047756800d585312a90a8523553c",
      "wav": "chunk-94.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 1051
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "text": "So which one are you running today? Vertical slices, or shared test folders?",
      "checksum": "sha256:44c65a5b38469ab8d68064b04006e230b31aa530316a9a7ac122b83d8bc43010",
      "wav": "chunk-95.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1060
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "text": "Drop your take in the comments. And then go run the brownfield-day-one skill on your codebase this weekend.",
      "checksum": "sha256:449970e9c1e20d6d3b8229fe5079cc18a95d03f73f8c74aff163ae13f607091a",
      "wav": "chunk-96.wav",
      "duration": 6.315827664399093,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 1073
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "text": "Ten minutes. You'll know more about your own repo than you do right now.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7b392ea540b9039c0dbed25491eed0bd726cd4d05a5d5853bac470c65ec33bf4",
      "wav": "chunk-97.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 1091
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "text": "If you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot AI community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ed8ab98bd7df91d3b58e78eff21993418ad4b085b0557e8f6564adfb92975283",
      "wav": "chunk-98.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 1105
    }
  ]
}